STATE
v.
OGLE 2018-1370 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 23, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appellant's motion for leave to file amended notice of appeal granted. Appellant's motion for leave to file amended memorandum in support of jurisdiction denied. Fischer, J., concurs.

French, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., would deny appellant's motion for leave to file amended notice of appeal.

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy and DeWine, JJ., would grant appellant's motion for leave to file amended memorandum in support of jurisdiction.
